'''威廉·「比爾」·坎登'''（{{lang-en|William "Bill" Condon}}，{{bd|1955年|10月22日}}）是一名[[美國|美國]]男編劇、導演和製片人。

== 早期生活 ==
比爾·坎登出生於[[紐約市|紐約市]]，父親是名[[偵探|偵探]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.filmreference.com/film/12/Bill-Condon.html |title=Bill Condon Biography (1956?-) |publisher=FilmReference.com |date=2000-10-06 |accessdate=2015-03-04 |archive-date=2019-10-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191013164517/http://www.filmreference.com/film/12/Bill-Condon.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他生長於一個[[愛爾蘭天主教|愛爾蘭天主教]]家庭<ref>{{cite web |last=Huttner |first=Jan Lisa |url=http://www.films42.com/chats/bill_condon.asp |title=Jan chats with Bill Condon |publisher=Films42.com |date=2004-11-19 |accessdate=2015-03-04 |archive-date=2016-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402125738/http://www.films42.com/chats/bill_condon.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他就讀了{{le|瑞吉高中 (紐約市)|Regis High School (New York City)|瑞吉高中}}與[[哥倫比亞學院|哥倫比亞學院]]，在那他學習了[[哲學|哲學]]。

== 個人生活 ==
比爾·坎登是名已[[出櫃|出櫃]]的[[同性戀|同性戀]]者<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.passportmagazine.com/departments/BillCondon.php |title=Bill Condon - Gay and Lesbian Travel |publisher=Passport Magazine |author=Lawrence Ferber |accessdate=2011-10-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120405210339/http://www.passportmagazine.com/departments/BillCondon.php |archivedate=2012-04-05 }}</ref>。他與傑克·莫里西（Jack Morrissey）是長期合作的夥伴<ref>{{cite web|last1=Teeman|first1=Tim|title=Can Condon's Freak Show Win Broadway?|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2014/11/18/can-bill-condon-s-freak-show-conquer-broadway.html|publisher=[[The_Daily_Beast|The Daily Beast]]|date=2014-11-18|accessdate=2015-11-02|archive-date=2018-02-10|archive-url=https://archive.today/20180210220742/https://www.thedailybeast.com/can-condons-freak-show-win-broadway|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Meet Jack Morrissey: Bill Condon’s Partner With Breaking Dawn Goodies|url=http://www.twilightlexicon.com/2011/07/09/meet-jack-morrissey-bill-condons-partner-with-breaking-dawn-goodies/|work=Twilight Lexicon|date=2011-07-09|accessdate=2015-11-02|archive-date=2019-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207215455/https://www.twilightlexicon.com/2011/07/09/meet-jack-morrissey-bill-condons-partner-with-breaking-dawn-goodies/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

